eautiful women to choose from, each unique and intriguing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animated racing scenes - make the right choices and win!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive phone system: chat, track character bios, receive spicy pictures, and more!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454570/extras/e89a153d434e7f8b1000ad44948a20a8.avif?t=1764251345\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p>", "short_description": "Race of Life is an adult visual novel. You play as Jake Miller, a divorced Professor who has taken up teaching after his past mistakes cost him his lucrative job and his marriage. When tragedy strikes, Jake must use every ounce of skill, smarts and ruthlessness to save the one he loves the most.", "supported_languages": "English, Simplified Chinese, Polish, Turkish, Russian, Italian, French, Spanish - Latin America, Traditional Chinese", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454570/header.jpg?t=1764251345", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1764251345", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1764251345", "website": "https://raceoflifegame.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7 or higher<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2,0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 or DirectX 9.0c compatible<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 9.0c<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 5 GB available space</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Req